":"a51b747882625f2fd921183b92a560025a48b226","tid":1644483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8235f3291d4340586b7a1851f787fa67ac006d","tid":1644483,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91dc4bafda75363500ed1368c8c4680e1f2bd0b0","tid":1644483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb00e791a2daee0f6e97b51a0fd0b2c740cf6f76","tid":1644483,"uid":193215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9w45Gb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9w45Gb.jpg&h=e53ed63c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"希望Trump後著係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:25:47.000Z","msg":"一定係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bf6becb0921cf7db45511f27f7da6fecc3143c","tid":1644483,"uid":201031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:32:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港人，學外交。特朗普在整蠱習近平，要習近平變相表態支持共和黨參選，否則下屆特朗普任期的時候，習近平有排難受了。<br />\n特朗普呼籲中國調查拜登父子在中國的貪污，習近平面有難色。拜登是前副總統，下屆美國總統選舉的民主黨總統呼聲最高的候選人。特朗普指控亨特於二〇一三年，曾跟隨拜登乘坐副總統專機到中國，亨特借助拜登的影響力，令自己的基金獲得巨額資金。<br />\n特朗普設定議題的智力高強，現在中國已經被佈局了，捲入美國的選舉裡面，而且是牌面上的捲入，不是牌底的捲入。以前的美國選舉，中國貿易和人權只是美國共和黨與民主黨辯論的議題，現在中國是捲入共和黨與民主黨的人事糾紛與醜聞裡面。早前，眾議院發言人佩羅西啟動彈劾案，調查特朗普總統在會見烏克蘭總統的時候施加壓力，要烏克蘭調查拜登父子在該國的貪污情況。<br />\n 習近平這個集大權於一身的末代昏君，怎麼應對美方的陷阱呢？一旦美國的總統大選將民主黨的貪污和華爾街的投共勾結暴露出來，中共在下一屆美國總統（好可能是特朗普當選）的任期內，更難受了。這就叫埋伏佈局（trap setting），而且要習近平自投羅網來向特朗普投誠，成為特朗普先生的nice friend。<br />\n這就是特朗普的議程設定能力（agenda setting），將中國牢牢打進選舉議題，不單止令民主黨要闢謠，而且要中共的賄賂美國政客行為成為共和黨競選的籌碼。習近平如果展開調查和提供證據，就是為特朗普提供彈藥整治自己；習近平如果不合作，那麼特朗普黑臉了，未來的五年任期，習近平更慘。<br />\n威脅敵國支持自己爭奪王位，繼續統治，否則用兵攻打。特朗普用的，近乎《春秋》時期的外交術了。我在星期日的國學班有講授的。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;陳雲談外交，香港建國要識得這些外交議程設定。不識得，只能讀陳雲面書偷師。之後說不是陳雲教的。<br />\n（閱讀智力門檻：IQ135.）"},{"pid":"da727d288b14a382300d022398a9fbf44c701346","tid":1644483,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"無人格的毒男開親post都陰陰濕濕暗中抹黑<br />\n好明顯係支那01班網軍<br />\n仲要係幾高級個隻<br />\n麻煩大家認下人名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人格的毒男</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3af87ef46ea5809e77d79f89e63933e270baaf1c","tid":1644483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da727d288b14a382300d022398a9fbf44c701346","tid":1644483,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"無人格的毒男開親post都陰陰濕濕暗中抹黑<br />\n好明顯係支那01班網軍<br />\n仲要係幾高級個隻<br />\n麻煩大家認下人名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人格的毒男</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>頂你個X. &nbsp; 唔好講我係香港01</strong></span><br />\n我通常貼毒果多, &nbsp;毒果貼我既料多過01. Ladj Ly單野又係毒果第一時間跟尾<br />\n<br />\n612同星火被抹黑, 我都第一時間撲火. &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我抹黑? &nbsp;抹黑條撚!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有. &nbsp;Michael Pillsbury而家認左中共有提供Joe Biden兒子Hunter Biden既料. 只係辯稱中共大部分俾既料都已經公開<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/trump-adviser-got-info-china-joe-biden-2019-10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-adviser-got-info-china-joe-biden-2019-10&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5T11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=9b635fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.businessinsider.com/trump-adviser-got-info-china-joe-biden-2019-10</a><br />\n<br />\nBut FT's Washington bureau chief released an email exchange between him and Pillsbury, in which Pillsbury wrote, &quot;Actually, I got quite a bit of background on Hunter Biden from the Chinese.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nShortly after that, Pillsbury gave another account, telling The Washington Post, &quot;Most everything I learned was already public or well known.&quot;"},{"pid":"206a2b802df19686014f3cf809379e820526d4a2","tid":1644483,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518ba17d8141b8735468be013b8c3f16d45d002e","tid":1644483,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"國會先係重點<br />\n侵侵一早準備用我地來DEAL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a3cbe1391e0c4be5da1dfad9810139e5caa742","tid":1644483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206a2b802df19686014f3cf809379e820526d4a2","tid":1644483,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518ba17d8141b8735468be013b8c3f16d45d002e","tid":1644483,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"國會先係重點<br />\n侵侵一早準備用我地來DEAL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"希望國會同官員夾實Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(路邊消息話Ted Cruz就快黎香港)"},{"pid":"af03ff2ceba2d26085a6fd41d00ffa965a903f90","tid":1644483,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28a3cbe1391e0c4be5da1dfad9810139e5caa742","tid":1644483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20